First Year Jaguars Owner Makes Rookie Mistake or Wise Business Move?

Alex Dunlap, Rosterwatch.com

New Jaguars owner Shahid Khan has an epic mustache and is an international Man of Mystery. To the shock of many, the league’s newest member of the Billionaire Boys Club got on board with GM Gene Smith to draft a punter with the Jaguars valuable #70 pick in this year’s NFL Draft, [a third round pick.] No punter has even gone in the Top 100 player selections in 17 years.
